\dfrac{\partial^2 u}{\partial x^2} = 6xy, \,\,u(0,y) = y, \,\,\dfrac{\partial u}{\partial x}(1,y)=0.
\displaystyle s^2\bar{u}(s,y)-su(0,y)-\frac{\partial u}{\partial x}(0,y) = \frac{6y}{s^2} \,\,\,\Longrightarrow\,\,\, \bar{u}(s,y)=sy +\frac{ 6y}{s^2}+\frac{\partial u}{\partial x}(0,y).
